[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0184","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0184.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0668","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 5 ActiveX 安全标记错误远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 5 中的 scriptlet.typelib ActiveX 控件被错误地标记为\"安全用于脚本\", 导致远程攻击者可通过诱导用户访问恶意网页, 利用该 ActiveX 控件执行任意命令(如 Bubbleboy 漏洞演示的文件写入攻击)。该漏洞影响 Microsoft Internet Explorer 5 版本, 攻击条件为用户访问恶意网页并启用 ActiveX, 攻击者可借此在用户系统上执行任意代码或写入文件, CVSS 评分 5.1, 属中危漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0668"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-08-21T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:48.493","remediation":"建议立即升级至 Internet Explorer 5.01 SP1 或更高版本，或安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-032 补丁（KB240308）；无法升级时可在 IE“Internet 区域”安全设置中将“运行未标记为安全的 ActiveX 控件”设为“禁用”，或为 scriptlet.typelib (CLSID: 06290BD5-48AA-11D2-8432-006008C3FBFC) 设置 Kill Bit 禁用该 ActiveX 控件","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/j-064.shtml","http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ240308","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/598","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-032","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19468","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/8d0ba8eaeba3ff3558e6044a19d5b454dcc12f33/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0668.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0668","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0668.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/512c773c61886081b2589de76a8cfde795349819/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0668.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/3c5965e4a3ad0d0b437f880f71224c9e3d8d5fd5/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-mf4v-53v8-r6cm/GHSA-mf4v-53v8-r6cm.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/178b809924783e13787d17bb1b1fd55ad3b8639b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0668.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--1311b123-7ec1-4ac2-beca-9860a9f96c2e.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0184.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0184.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0184.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1188","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1188.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1565","title":"man2html 临时文件符号链接攻击 任意文件写入漏洞","description":"tags.<value>Man2html 2.1 及更早版本存在任意文件写入漏洞，原因在于程序在处理临时文件时未对文件路径进行充分的安全校验。本地攻击者可利用符号链接（symlink）攻击，将临时文件重定向到系统中的任意文件路径，从而覆盖敏感文件或写入恶意内容，最终可能导致权限提升或系统稳定性受损。该漏洞影响所有使用 man2html 2.1 及更早版本的 Linux/Unix 系统，需要具备本地访问权限才能进行利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1565"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-20T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:43.720","remediation":"立即升级 man2html 至 2.2 或更高版本，该版本已使用 mkstemp() 等安全函数创建临时文件，修复了通过符号链接覆盖任意文件的问题。如暂时无法升级，可通过包管理器安装系统安全更新（如 Debian/Ubuntu 执行 apt upgrade man2html，RHEL/CentOS 执行 yum update man2html），或临时移除 man2html 的 setuid/setgid 权限（chmod u-s,g-s $(which man2html)）以缓解本地提权风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/6291","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/24784","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/770e8f09ce14e637a09c7c619e10772aa6172bea/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1565.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1565","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-1565.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/12e9f9121122940a38e93216069cda4e01d5b051/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1565.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/2a2be81fd4b47dc35d815a995b6429bd116a3b84/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-xq33-vcxx-f474/GHSA-xq33-vcxx-f474.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87953/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/178b809924783e13787d17bb1b1fd55ad3b8639b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1565.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153600_153700.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000739.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1188.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1184","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1184.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1561","title":"Nullsoft SHOUTcast服务器权限许可和访问控制漏洞","description":"Nullsoft SHOUTcast 服务器将管理员密码以明文形式存储在配置文件 sc_serv.conf 中，本地攻击者可通过读取该配置文件获取管理员凭据，进而获得服务器管理权限。该漏洞影响 SHOUTcast 服务器软件，攻击者需具有本地文件系统访问权限才能利用，属于权限许可和访问控制缺陷，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1561"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-20T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:43.237","remediation":"将 sc_serv.conf 配置文件权限设为仅运行 SHOUTcast 的服务账户可读写（如 chmod 600 并归运行用户所有），禁止其他本地用户访问；升级到 Nullsoft 发布的修复版本（1.9.8 及以上，使用加密或独立认证机制）；在暂无法升级时，将服务器进程以受限低权限专用账户运行，并通过防火墙限制 8000 管理端口仅允许可信 IP 访问，避免明文密码被本地其他用户读取。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/24852","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/770e8f09ce14e637a09c7c619e10772aa6172bea/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1561.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1561","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-1561.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/e1298ff7aafe81b936ca67ecef34c3124d6c72f0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1561.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/2a2be81fd4b47dc35d815a995b6429bd116a3b84/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3p7f-hw68-ph5v/GHSA-3p7f-hw68-ph5v.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87926/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/178b809924783e13787d17bb1b1fd55ad3b8639b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1561.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/c10333c2a2ff64c06fea798156aba12d16cb8ad5/1999.tsv","https://github.com/Yuning-J/NVDFeatureAnalysis/blob/493a57a415cc110f9945148abd717eeb92f6ca7e/originalDataset/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1184.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0364","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0364.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0743","title":"Trn 本地用户符号链接覆盖其他用户文件漏洞","description":"Trn 新闻阅读器存在本地符号链接漏洞，本地用户可通过创建符号链接指向其他用户文件，在特定条件下覆盖目标文件内容。该漏洞源于程序在处理临时文件时未对符号链接进行充分校验，攻击者需要拥有本地系统访问权限，利用难度较低但影响范围有限（仅影响同系统用户），CVSS 评分 2.1 危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0743"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-08-20T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:57.870","remediation":"升级 Trn 至修复了不安全临时文件创建的版本（trn 4.0-test77 之后版本），或在 Linux 内核中通过 fs.protected_symlinks=1 启用符号链接保护（sysctl -w fs.protected_symlinks=1）。如无法升级，建议将 /tmp 挂载为 noexec,nosuid 并使用 private /tmp 模式（systemd 默认启用），同时在 cron 中定期清理 /tmp 下的 Trn 临时文件。使用 tmpfiles.d 或 pam_namespace 对每位用户隔离临时目录可彻底阻断此类攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3144","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e6f80460dd56d97b6079eb72c9467b9a961ce1b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0743.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0743","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0743.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0743.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-w5gh-xpm5-prq2/GHSA-w5gh-xpm5-prq2.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0743.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88064/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--f7f02ce6-65e9-4ce7-aacb-b8528cfb6e7e.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0364.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0555","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0555.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0741","title":"QMS CrownNet Unix 认证绕过漏洞","description":"QMS CrownNet Unix Utilities for 2060 存在严重身份认证绕过漏洞，系统默认允许 root 用户无需密码即可直接登录，攻击者可通过 telnet 或 rlogin 等远程访问服务利用该漏洞获取目标系统的超级用户权限。该漏洞影响 QMS CrownNet 2060 系列设备，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重，攻击复杂度低且无需认证，可导致设备完全受控。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0741"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-08-19T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:57.630","remediation":"建议立即升级 QMS CrownNet Unix Utilities 至修复版本（需联系 QMS 获取补丁），或在 /etc/securetty 中禁止 root 远程登录，同时配置 PAM 认证强制要求密码验证。若设备已停止维护，请部署网络隔离并限制 515 端口仅允许受信 IP 访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/593","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/f54846af4ec1affce3d519a6791531e8f1f5b8fe/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0741.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0741","https://github.com/fankh/vulnerability-poc/blob/939392c6c114126badd68bf811168babfcf07fe3/1999/CVE-1999-0741/README.md","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0741.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/cf6074d8ac2128dee0a2ac26c5f652ae6527df79/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0741.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/8b1565557a8e0fb04634f0989d7e7dd7febd4847/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-hmmr-pvfg-gcfv/GHSA-hmmr-pvfg-gcfv.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/178b809924783e13787d17bb1b1fd55ad3b8639b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0741.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0555.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0506","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0506.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0725","title":"Microsoft IIS 3.0/4.0 双字节代码页源代码泄露漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 3.0 和 4.0 在将默认语言配置为简体中文、韩文或日文等双字节代码页（Double Byte Code Page）时，存在源代码泄露漏洞。由于服务器对双字节字符编码的处理不当，远程攻击者在无需身份认证的情况下，可通过构造包含特定双字节字符序列的 HTTP 请求访问 ASP 等动态脚本文件，使服务器错误解析请求并返回这些文件的源代码而非执行结果。该漏洞影响所有以中文、日文或韩文为默认语言运行的 IIS 3.0/4.0 网站，攻击条件仅为目标站点启用相应双字节代码页且可直接网络访问，攻击者利用浏览器或脚本即可远程触发，进而可能泄露数据库凭据、内部逻辑等敏感信息。Microsoft 已通过后续安全更新修复此问题。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0725"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-08-19T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:55.577","remediation":"立即为受影响的 IIS 3.0 或 IIS 4.0 服务器应用 Microsoft Security Bulletin MS99-022 的安全补丁，补丁对应知识库文章 KB233335（标题：Page Contents Visible When Certain Characters are at End of URL）。请注意：补丁的语言版本应与 IIS 安装的语言版本相匹配，而非服务器当前默认语言版本；若已安装 IIS 4.0 补丁且存在回归错误，请下载 1999 年 8 月 19 日重新发布的修正版本。最根本的修复方案是将 IIS 升级至 5.0 或更高版本。如暂时无法打补丁，可将服务器默认语言从中文、日文或韩文更改为英文作为临时缓解措施，或通过 URLScan 工具过滤包含双字节字符的特制 URL 请求，防止服务器绕过处理并将文件以纯文本形式返回给浏览器。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ233335","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/477","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-022","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2302","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19361","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0f25967d744704fe14324ac10f2b57e945aed081/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0725.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0725","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d2eb55660fa7a900eec90103b031be5d6f98d9ec/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0725.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0725.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/178b809924783e13787d17bb1b1fd55ad3b8639b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0725.json","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/6b04404d068dfd5fefed82d0ee9143755d472917/1999/CVE-1999-0725.json","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/ec2efce98d544aa857266906f720ae32e42b21be/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-07xx/CVE-1999-0725.json","https://github.com/CyberSecAI/cve_info/blob/03b7e36424574a3a9ba5fd13480a326b666a1046/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0725.json","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelist-dev/blob/5b8fbb570438e8094550205589cc6f1d122acc94/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0725.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0725.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0506.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0358","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0358.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0740","title":"Red Hat Linux in.telnetd TERM 环境变量畸形数据拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Red Hat Linux 4.2/5.2/6.0 系统中的 telnet 远程服务存在环境变量处理漏洞。该漏洞源于 in.telnetd 程序在处理客户机发送的 TERM 环境变量时未能对其进行充分验证，导致当目标系统接收到特定格式的 TERM 环境变量时，远程攻击者可利用该漏洞触发服务崩溃进程，使得 telnet 服务无法正常响应。从属于 TCP 的网络服务，运行在各种 LINUX/UNIX 操作系统中。攻击者可通过向 telnet 服务发送特定格式的环境变量数据包，触发该漏洞，造成目标服务器上的 telnet 远程服务完全宕机，导致用户无法远程登录系统。该漏洞为远程拒绝服务型漏洞，攻击者无需任何权限即可远程触发，仅需在攻击过程中发送一个特定的 TERM 环境变量即可。该漏洞对远程 telnet 服务访问的网络服务构成严重威胁，影响整个网络服务的可用性。 telent 远程服务在 Red Hat Linux 4.2/5.2/6.0 版本中普遍存在，而 Red Hat Linux 的广泛应用使得大量网络服务器面临风险。该漏洞的 CVSS 评分为 6.4，威胁等级为中危。相关安全厂商已发布安全公告，建议用户升级到更高版本以获取修复补丁。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0740"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-08-19T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:57.517","remediation":"建议立即禁用 telnet 服务（chkconfig telnet off 并重启 xinetd），迁移至 SSH 替代远程管理。受影响的 Red Hat Linux 4.2/5.2/6.0 均已停止维护，建议升级至受支持的 RHEL 8/9 或其他现代发行版。若短期内无法升级，可通过 iptables 限制 23 端口的访问源 IP，仅允许可信网段连接，降低被攻击风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/594","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/f54846af4ec1affce3d519a6791531e8f1f5b8fe/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0740.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0740","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0740.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/cf6074d8ac2128dee0a2ac26c5f652ae6527df79/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0740.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/8b1565557a8e0fb04634f0989d7e7dd7febd4847/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-chv2-pxjh-365q/GHSA-chv2-pxjh-365q.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0740.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_dos.txt","https://github.com/VulnerabilityHistoryProject/mega-foss/blob/4829eeb7b0101570abbc87d2a697f2c0c2f4e5c3/src/cve/graphql/trial.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0358.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0345","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0345.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0732","title":"Debian smtp-refuser 日志记录本地任意文件删除漏洞","description":"Debian smtp-refuser 软件包的日志记录功能存在不安全符号链接处理漏洞。本地攻击者可通过创建符号链接将日志文件重定向指向系统任意文件，利用日志写入操作删除目标文件，造成拒绝服务或本地权限提升。该漏洞需本地用户权限方可利用，攻击条件受限，影响 Debian 系统中的 smtp-refuser 软件包。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0732"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-08-19T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:56.500","remediation":"Debian 已移除 smtp-refuser 软件包，建议迁移至 Postfix 或 Exim 等现代 MTA。若仍需使用，需将日志目录所有权设为专用系统用户，且日志文件创建时使用 O_EXCL 标志防止跟随符号链接，同时以低权限用户运行守护进程。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0732","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/f4ffb7bcd93209aa53a757a7ebdf17fe2a18eb33/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0732.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0732","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0732.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0732.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-rh82-9f2f-4h42/GHSA-rh82-9f2f-4h42.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/bc3b224aa865bb4a5c31d7720dca83e446e475e2/1999/CVE-1999-0732.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88036/info.html","https://github.com/debiancn/debian.org/blob/6abc98daa6356b20e410013a6920b3764af682d4/english/security/1999/19990823b.data","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--fc08d088-1503-41d7-bd11-adf99800d367.json","https://github.com/VulnerabilityHistoryProject/mega-foss/blob/4829eeb7b0101570abbc87d2a697f2c0c2f4e5c3/src/cve/graphql/trial.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0345.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0348","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0348.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0734","title":"CiscoSecure 访问控制服务器（ACS）默认配置未授权访问漏洞","description":"CiscoSecure访问控制服务器（ACS）for UNIX在默认安装配置下缺乏必要的身份验证机制。未经身份认证的远程攻击者无需提供任何凭据，即可直接通过TCP端口9900访问并修改ACS服务器的内部数据库，包括用户账户、访问控制策略及认证配置等敏感数据。该漏洞影响CiscoSecure ACS for UNIX 1.0至2.3.2版本，攻击者可利用此漏洞篡改安全策略、创建未授权账户或植入后门，从而完全绕过企业网络的访问控制体系。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0734"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-19","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级 CiscoSecure ACS for UNIX 至 2.3.3 或更高版本，该版本默认已启用管理客户端验证。如无法升级，可编辑 CSCconfig.ini 配置文件，设置 ValidateClients=true 并在 [ValidClients] 段中仅允许受信管理主机的 IP 或主机名；同时在网络防火墙上限制对 TCP 端口 9900 的访问，仅允许受信管理网络连接。注意：2.2.2、2.2.3、2.3.1 和 2.3.2 版本启用客户端验证后会影响管理 GUI 功能，建议直接升级至 2.3.3。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://tools.cisco.com/security/center/content/CiscoSecurityAdvisory/cisco-sa-19990819-dbaccess","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3133","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0734"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0348.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0600","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0600.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0745","title":"IBM AIX pdnsd 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"IBM AIX 4.1 及 4.2 版本的 C Set++ 编译器所附带的源码浏览器程序数据库名称服务守护进程（pdnsd）存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的网络请求触发该溢出，进而在无需身份认证的情况下执行任意代码或导致服务拒绝。由于 pdnsd 以较高权限运行，成功利用后可完全控制系统，影响范围涵盖运行受影响版本 AIX 的系统。该漏洞 CVSS v2 评分为 10.0，危害等级为严重。IBM 已发布相应安全公告及补丁程序修复此问题。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0745"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-08-18T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:58.130","remediation":"建议升级到 IBM 官方发布的 C Set ++ 编译器补丁版本，安装 pdnsd 相关 APAR 修复补丁。若无法及时升级，应限制或禁用 Source Code Browser 的 pdnsd 守护进程，通过防火墙限制其网络访问，仅允许可信主机连接，并以最小权限运行该服务以降低缓冲区溢出被利用的风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-059.shtml","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/590","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/21093","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/184a5a0fb7dfcbb1c5bcfd5178078c78dc1e4738/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0745.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0745","https://github.com/fankh/vulnerability-poc/blob/70aa1195d82bd1159a5a1aff1d7bd9099bc900b6/1999/CVE-1999-0745/README.md","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0745.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/95eeda559fd899397df50f658cf25cf01bb1e4ea/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0745.json","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/1261.txt","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/sid-msg.map","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0745.json","https://github.com/jdkoftinoff/mb-linux-msli/blob/8adb103e34af9ff1d8d122e9ee2a1808836f0a14/uClinux-dist/user/snort/drop-rules/exploit.rules","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0600.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0600.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0600.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0381","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0381.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0747","title":"BSDi Symmetric Multiprocessing 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"BSDi Symmetric Multiprocessing (SMP) 系统存在拒绝服务漏洞。当系统处于高 CPU 负载状态时，本地攻击者可通过调用 fstat 系统函数触发该漏洞，导致系统拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 BSDi SMP 版本，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。攻击者需要具有本地访问权限且系统处于高负载状态才能利用此漏洞。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0747"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-08-18T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:58.370","remediation":"升级到 BSDi 的 SMP 补丁版本（如 BSD/OS 4.0.1 或更高），该版本已修复高 CPU 负载下 fstat 调用导致的拒绝服务问题。由于 BSDi 操作系统已停止维护，建议迁移至受支持的现代操作系统（如 FreeBSD 或 Linux）以获取持续安全更新。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/589","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&msg=Pine.BSI.4.10.9908170253560.19291-100000%40saturn.psn.net"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0381.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0606","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0606.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0753","title":"Hughes Technologies Mini SQL 信息泄露漏洞","description":"Hughes Technologies Mini SQL (mSQL) 2.0 及 2.0.10 版本存在信息泄露漏洞，攻击者无需身份认证即可通过网络连接默认 1114 端口访问数据库服务，发送特定查询或访问默认开放的管理接口，从而读取数据库结构、用户表及系统配置等敏感元数据。该漏洞源于 mSQL 服务器在处理查询请求时未正确实施访问控制，导致未授权用户可获取敏感信息，可能造成数据泄露并为后续渗透提供条件。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0753"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-17","updated":"1999-08-17","remediation":"升级到 mSQL 2.0.11 或后续已修复版本；若无法升级，应在防火墙层面限制 1114 端口仅允许可信本地或内网地址访问，禁用默认管理接口并移除匿名查询权限，避免将数据库端口直接暴露于公网。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19466","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/76af88afbb282d6c9e8ce3b9f6942bcb7e39be57/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0753.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0606.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0606.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0606.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0386","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0386.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0749","title":"Microsoft Windows 95/98 Telnet客户端堆溢出漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows 95 和 Windows 98 系统自带的 Telnet 客户端存在堆缓冲区溢出漏洞。当该客户端处理构造畸形的 Telnet 参数（如过长的命令行参数或特制的参数数据）时，由于缺乏充分的边界校验，会导致堆内存被覆盖。本地或远程的攻击者可通过诱导受害者使用恶意构造的 Telnet 参数（例如通过网页中的恶意链接或脚本调用 Telnet 客户端）触发此漏洞，可能造成客户端崩溃或在受影响系统上执行任意代码。该漏洞影响运行 Windows 95 与 Windows 98 并包含 Telnet 客户端的系统，攻击需借助社会工程诱导用户触发，利用门槛相对较高，CVSS 评分为 2.6，危害等级较低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0749"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-08-16T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:58.607","remediation":"建议立即升级至受支持的 Windows 版本（如 Windows 10/11），Windows 95/98 已停止支持且无官方补丁。若必须继续使用旧系统，请立即卸载或禁用 Telnet 客户端（控制面板→添加/删除程序→Windows 组件→取消勾选 Telnet 客户端），并改用 SSH 等加密协议替代明文 Telnet。网络层面在防火墙层面封禁 TCP 23 端口入站/出站，防止恶意 Telnet 参数触发堆溢出。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/586","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-033","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19462","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/cf29b986be3ae7c9144123b101d864868676099e/1999/CVE-1999-0749.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/184a5a0fb7dfcbb1c5bcfd5178078c78dc1e4738/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0749.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0749","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/95eeda559fd899397df50f658cf25cf01bb1e4ea/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0749.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0749.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/8b1565557a8e0fb04634f0989d7e7dd7febd4847/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-68h4-pjm9-c4qv/GHSA-68h4-pjm9-c4qv.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/178b809924783e13787d17bb1b1fd55ad3b8639b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0749.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0386.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0386.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0386.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0379","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0379.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0746","title":"SuSE Linux in.identd 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"SuSE Linux 6.2 及更早版本中随附的 in.identd 服务在默认配置下，对来自同一来源的请求之间会强制等待约 120 秒。远程攻击者无需身份认证，只需持续向目标主机的 ident 服务（TCP 113 端口）发送大量或连续的连接请求，即可耗尽服务端的连接处理能力，使 in.identd 长时间无法响应合法的身份查询请求，从而造成拒绝服务（DoS）。该漏洞影响运行 SuSE Linux 6.2 及以下版本且启用默认 in.identd 配置的系统，攻击条件仅需网络可达目标 113 端口，利用方式简单，可通过自动化脚本批量发起连接触发。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0746"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-08-16T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:58.247","remediation":"建议立即将 SuSE Linux 升级到 6.3 及以上版本，该版本已修复 in.identd 默认配置缺陷。如暂时无法升级，可修改 /etc/inetd.conf 中 ident 服务配置，将 in.identd 的超时等待时间由默认 120 秒调小（如添加 -t 或 -o 超时参数），或在防火墙/inetd 层面限制对 113 端口的外部连接，仅允许可信内网访问，以此缓解远程拒绝服务风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/587","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19463","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/184a5a0fb7dfcbb1c5bcfd5178078c78dc1e4738/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0746.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0746","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0746.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/95eeda559fd899397df50f658cf25cf01bb1e4ea/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0746.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/8b1565557a8e0fb04634f0989d7e7dd7febd4847/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-868p-j55q-vf55/GHSA-868p-j55q-vf55.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/Freem93/grammar_nasl_v2/blob/63834ebb8cd6e97050e155291c7500ad53bb20c6/plugins/suse_identd.nasl","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_2.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0379.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0225","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0225.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0679","title":"EFnet Hybrid IRCd 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"EFnet 常用的 hybrid-6 IRC 服务器存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向服务器发送特制的 m_invite invite 选项触发该漏洞，导致任意代码执行。该漏洞影响 Hybrid Ircd 5.0.3 p7 及更早版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用，成功利用后可完全控制目标服务器。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0679"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-08-13T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:49.900","remediation":"升级 hybrid-ircd 至 6.0 或更高版本，该漏洞已在后续版本中修复。如无法升级，可在 IRC 服务器配置中禁用 m_invite 命令或限制远程用户的 invite 权限作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.efnet.org/archive/servers/hybrid/ChangeLog","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/581","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19459","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b620a68f213580a6ffea66162a8ff5e007fc8af7/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0679.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0679","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0679.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/6cc69bd737a75cf8d608267baabc212a8abe28cf/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0679.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/ab4d5447f6ae2c4c3eb5c082fd4adfb5e47fd740/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3c24-mx8q-qwqm/GHSA-3c24-mx8q-qwqm.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0679.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--53a24dd1-2f0b-4489-8912-d13ab5816b7a.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000727.txt","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_overflow.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0225.toml"}]